狗學校, 俾佢同多d狗互動<br />\n<br />\nbtw adopt, don't buy</blockquote><br />\n德牧 秋田呢啲你唔由細黎<br />\n到時教嗰陣你就真係知味道</blockquote><br />\n德牧呢d服從性咁高真係要由細養起 由細養起就算無咩點train都好聽話 好保護主人</blockquote><br />\n狗b都有得adopt嘅, 有朋友喺狗場救過狗媽同一胎五隻b<br />\n分分鐘你去買同你領養嘅係同一隻b<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4ad8018eb61ebaa591512204e5d9aaffc367c14","tid":166081,"uid":21392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T04:51:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>本身養開隻金毛(仔，7歲大)，幾個月前<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">買左</span></span>隻2個月大既德牧(女)，想同隻金毛做伴同埋希望佢以後幫手睇下門口。<br />\n<br />\n[img][url]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/Ej65Gou.jpg[img][/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEj65Gou.jpg%5Bimg%5D%5B%2Furl%5D&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=8bd3616f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/Ej65Gou.jpg[img][/url]</a><br />\n[img][url]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/14p97fO.jpg[img][/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F14p97fO.jpg%5Bimg%5D%5B%2Furl%5D&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=2b12b547\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/14p97fO.jpg[img][/url]</a><br />\n<br />\n點知而家養左3個月，發現佢超無膽，咩都驚 (以前隻金毛同年都無咁細膽)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽到聲就跑返入屋，見到其他狗同人想行埋黎就即使衝去我身後面，連見到一隻玩具熊都驚到對住佢係咁叫，成日咩都要跟住隻大狗<br />\n<br />\n網上睇話係無自信既表現<br />\n<br />\n[img][url]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/2J1C2FG.jpg[img][/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2J1C2FG.jpg%5Bimg%5D%5B%2Furl%5D&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=81268256\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/2J1C2FG.jpg[img][/url]</a><br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲有經驗同方法點提高佢自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做乜撚嘢啫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nD狗撚係咁弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全世界都要領養先比養狗咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5fdfd1c104e8b9d964670610d42b4b539285f26","tid":166081,"uid":21392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T04:52:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係連登講買狗你仆街了...下次唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利伸: 下星期準備返大陸食狗肉</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nChing一齊"},{"pid":"d33cc2012adff7349e4bfeed690c2ef0176cd7c2","tid":166081,"uid":21392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T04:52:48.000Z","msg":"帶佢去屌